text: Harmeet Singh Sandhu is an Indian politician. He belongs to the Shiromani Akali Dal party. He is a former member of the Punjab Legislative Assembly and represented Tarn Taran from 2002 to 2017.Punjab data entry on Tarn Taran district == References == == Other websites == http://eciresults.nic.in/ConstituencywiseS1921.htm?ac=21 Category:Politicians from Punjab, India Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
